---
export const prerender = true;
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | PropDiscover"
  description="Read the Privacy Policy for PropDiscover to understand how we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
>
  <section class="py-14 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: May 10, 2026</p>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 p-6 md:p-8 space-y-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          PropDiscover values your privacy. This page explains what information we collect, how we use it, and how we protect it when you use our website.
        </p>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>We may collect your name, phone number, email address, and project preferences when you submit forms or contact us.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">How We Use Information</h2>
          <p>We use your details to respond to inquiries, share relevant property information, and improve user experience on the platform.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Data Security</h2>
          <p>We implement reasonable technical and organizational safeguards to protect your information from unauthorized access.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p>Our site may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for their privacy practices or content.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Policy Updates</h2>
          <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated date.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Contact</h2>
          <p>For privacy-related questions, contact us at <a class="text-primary-700 hover:text-primary-800" href="mailto:support@propdiscover.com">support@propdiscover.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
